container_info.post_install_tip: Go to "Add-ons > BigML > Start" and a sidebar will appear. Set your credentials to see your models or clusters in BigML. Choose a model or cluster. Highlight the cells to be used as input and click Predict to fill the blanks with predictions or labels.

name: BigML
description: The BigML add-on provides an easy way to fill the blanks in your Spreadsheets using the predictions of models and clusters in BigML.
